**11. Viết code Day 1**

File [main.jsx](c:/Users/toann/Desktop/PHP/SneakerStore_USER/frontend-react/src/main.jsx)

```jsx
import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App'
import './index.css'

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>,
)
```

Giải thích:
- `ReactDOM.createRoot(...)`: tạo root React
- `document.getElementById('root')`: trỏ vào `div#root` trong `index.html`
- `render(<App />)`: render component `App`

File [App.jsx](c:/Users/toann/Desktop/PHP/SneakerStore_USER/frontend-react/src/App.jsx)

```jsx
import Header from './components/Header'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import Footer from './components/Footer'
import HomePage from './pages/HomePage'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Navbar />
      <main className="container">
        <HomePage />
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </>
  )
}
```

Giải thích:
- `App` là component gốc
- `<> ... </>` là `Fragment`
- `Fragment` dùng để bọc nhiều component mà không sinh thêm thẻ HTML thừa

File [Header.jsx](c:/Users/toann/Desktop/PHP/SneakerStore_USER/frontend-react/src/components/Header.jsx)

